{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to conceptual definitions, we also provide operational definitions.",
    "That is, in addition to clarifying what a term means, we also explain how the respective theoretical construct has been or could be measured or manipulated.",
    "In some cases, different words are used for the same construct, and we provide a list of synonyms.",
    "The paper is divided into three sections: Part 1 (essays), Part 2 (glossary), and Appendix (genesis).",
    "Part 1 consists of several essays on what we refer to as clusters of terms, that is, terms that are strongly related and often obtain their meaning in relation to each other (see Table 1 for a list of these clusters)."
  ]
}